<Title>OFCR/OFAR Oxygen Controllers</Title>
<MELSubItem itemNbr="35-21-05-01">
<Title>Seat/Bunk Controllers</Title>
<DispatchCondition dispCondOptions="A" repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="9" nbrRequired="0" maintIndicator="(M)">
<Title>Seat/Bunk Blocked</Title>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>Applicable to: VN-A861, VN-A862, VN-A863, VN-A864, VN-A867, VN-A868, VN-A870, VN-A871.</Para>
<Para>May be inoperative provided associated seat/bunk is blocked and placarded to prevent occupancy.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Block and placard associated seat/bunk (AMM DDG 35-21-05).</Para>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
<DispatchCondition dispCondOptions="B" repairInterval="C" nbrInstalled="9" nbrRequired="0" opsIndicator="(O)">
<Title>Altitude Restrictions Are Applied</Title>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>Applicable to: VN-A861, VN-A862, VN-A863, VN-A864, VN-A867, VN-A868, VN-A870, VN-A871.</Para>
<Para>May be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Appropriate portable oxygen supplies are available.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Both air conditioning packs operate normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Pressurization system operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Appropriate altitude adjustments are applied.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Crew are appropriately briefed.</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
